+-----------------------------------------+
| bunsen-exit-ng - a suckless exit dialog |
+-----------------------------------------+

0. INSTALLATION

Install the prerequisites:

  * dmenuv (see https://github.com/2ion/dmenu-v)
  * GNU coreutils
  * bash

Clone the repository:

  git clone --branch dmenuv --single-branch https://github.com/2ion/bunsen-exit-ng.git

Install dmenu-v, bunsen-exit-ng and the exitrc configuration file:

  make install PREFIX=/usr/local
  make install-exitrc EXITRC=$HOME/.exitrc # goes into your home directory

1. CONFIGURATION

Configure the commands, font, bar position and other stuff in ~/.exitrc.

Use xselfont for obtaining a X11 font specification.

Now you can run bunsen-exit-ng.


